France Volontaire and the Volunteering Space for Vietnam and Laos invite you to join our event, the French Volunteer Day.

This event will take place at AFD/EFEO gardens in Ho Chi Minh City (113 Hai Ba Trung, Ben Nghe, D1). 

Come to join us and discover how the international NGO and local NPO create good conditions for a sustainable development of Vietnam! 

Conference, fair and photo exhibition are in the program!